# ModSecurity connector local lighttpd extension
#
# Target: lighttpd 1.4.84 source tree only.
# ABI: LIGHTTPD_MSCONNECTOR_STREAM_HOOK_ABI_VERSION=1.
#
# This is deliberately incompatible with stock dynamic modules.  It adds
# synchronous, borrowed request-body and HTTP/1.x entity-body/EOS callbacks.
# The response hook runs before HTTP/1 transfer framing, not in the socket
# queue. HTTP/2 is intentionally excluded because its connection queue
# contains multiplexed framed bytes. EAGAIN and short writes happen after the
# one-time entity callback, so they cannot duplicate body inspection.
#
