+	/*
+	 * Borrowed, synchronous body ranges for this local ABI extension.
+	 * Request callbacks visit a lighttpd-owned queue range.  Response
+	 * callbacks receive a current HTTP/1.x entity-body range before transfer
+	 * encoding is added. `stream_offset` is monotonic.  Callbacks must not
+	 * retain bytes, mutate queues, or perform deferred access. A NULL data
+	 * pointer is valid only for an empty response EOS notification.
